，先向天開一槍，再向職員開兩槍，幸而沒有打中。<br />\n<br />\n翌日早上，警員去到薩布羅斯基的住所附近，他欲駕駛貨車逃走時被截停；他跳出車廂並拿出一支AK-47及一支半自動手槍，與至少7名警員激烈駁火，最終薩布羅斯基的腿及臀部中槍，受傷被捕。他被控謀殺未遂、嚴重襲擊及搶劫等22項罪名，當局批准他以100萬美元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯的代表律師沃爾德倫(John Waldron)表示，薩布羅斯基最近失業及失去孩子的監護權，對於疫情感到難以承受，但他坦言薩布羅斯基拿著重型武器與警方駁火，只中兩槍而保住命仔，已經非常好彩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgDFCbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgDFCbX.jpg&h=dd1d983c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYKhEqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYKhEqh.jpg&h=d2a50938&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"廢老吐口水就贏啦"},{"pid":"f48df62e485f0a5c68833b205ce1d5163a5c080c","tid":2140913,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80c0de1b8a9ff000d6186db2477cbcd664172f80","tid":2140913,"uid":59328,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"33de08f924fdef59378a9bcff76fde94266ff8c2","tid":2140913,"uid":288071,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"redneck真係同nigga無分別"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"連登當redneck神咁拜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a093d59a74d76df8d024272a50feaaab1b8c598","tid":2140913,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔： 美國人由細到大享受自由，點同香港既奴隸"},{"pid":"3defb7a091c5f9ee41619b05aabfaff832c3f521","tid":2140913,"uid":142686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"熱狗：好波！最好射撚死個員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062e33adca1fa1ab7bdbfb47e26796e6cc173e2a","tid":2140913,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"白色可以反射，黑色會吸收，呢啲物理常識"},{"pid":"cb6f174b39645c6e377c49340b5651b1ad97cb2a","tid":2140913,"uid":224916,"like":2,"dislike":0